fast, scalable, and cost-effective platform for developers.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"16\",{\"name\":\"twitter:image\",\"content\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/frontend/gptproto/images-8e534625-2156-4fd8-a0aa-704f773f119c.png\"}]],\"error\":null,\"digest\":\"$undefined\"}\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"11:\"$c:metadata\"\n15:T12744,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"url\":\"https://gptproto.com\",\"description\":\"All-In-One AI APIs and AI Models for Developers\",\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/13/3120d7cbe1b34a4eb20cc08032c81968.png\"}}},{\"@type\":\"SoftwareApplication\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto API Platform\",\"applicationCategory\":\"DeveloperApplication\",\"operatingSystem\":\"Web, Cloud\",\"description\":\"Unified AI API platform providing access to multiple AI models including OpenAI GPT-4, Claude, Gemini, Midjourney, and more. All-in-one gateway for text, image, video, and audio AI generation.\",\"abstract\":\"The ultimate unified AI API platform aggregating DeepSeek, OpenAI, Claude, Midjourney, and more with standardized protocols and 60% lower costs.\",\"url\":\"https://gptproto.com\",\"featureList\":[\"Unified API Standard (OpenAI Compatible)\",\"Multi-model Aggregation (DeepSeek, Claude, Midjourney, etc.)\",\"Smart Resource Scheduling\",\"Cost-effective Pricing (approx. 60% of official rates)\"],\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"lowPrice\":\"5\",\"highPrice\":\"1000\",\"offerCount\":\"5\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\",\"priceSpecification\":[{\"@type\":\"UnitPriceSpecification\",\"price\":\"5\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"name\":\"Starter Plan\"},{\"@type\":\"UnitPriceSpecification\",\"price\":\"50\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"name\":\"Standard Plan\"},{\"@type\":\"UnitPriceSpecification\",\"price\":\"100\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"name\":\"Professional Plan\"},{\"@type\":\"UnitPriceSpecification\",\"price\":\"500\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"name\":\"Business Plan\"},{\"@type\":\"UnitPriceSpecification\",\"price\":\"1000\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"name\":\"Enterprise Plan\"}]},\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":\"4.8\",\"ratingCount\":\"500\",\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"worstRating\":\"1\"},\"audience\":{\"@type\":\"Audience\",\"audienceType\":\"Developers, Business Teams, Enterprise Clients\"},\"provider\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\"}},{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"alternateName\":\"GPTProto\",\"url\":\"https://gptproto.com\",\"logo\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/13/3120d7cbe1b34a4eb20cc08032c81968.png\",\"description\":\"Access powerful AI APIs and models with GPT Proto, including OpenAI, Claude, Gemini, and more. A fast, scalable, and cost-effective platform for developers.\",\"slogan\":\"Unified API Aggregation Platform for Global Top-tier AI Models\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\"},\"sameAs\":[\"https://x.com/gptproto\",\"https://www.pinterest.com/gptproto/\",\"https://github.com/gptprotoofficial\",\"https://medium.com/@gptproto.official\",\"https://substack.com/@gptproto1\",\"https://www.producthunt.com/@gptproto_official\",\"https://www.instagram.com/gptproto.official/\",\"https://www.threads.com/@gptproto.official\",\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/gptproto/\",\"https://www.youtube.com/@GPTProtoOfficial\"],\"contactPoint\":{\"@type\":\"ContactPoint\",\"contactType\":\"Customer Support\",\"email\":\"gptproto.official@gmail.com\",\"availableLanguage\":[\"English\",\"Chinese\"]}},{\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"GPT Proto: The Global Unified API Aggregation Platform for Leading AI Models\",\"url\":\"https://gptproto.com/\",\"image\":\"https://gptproto.com/assets/images/gptproto-cover.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2024-12-11\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://gptproto.com/assets/images/logo.png\"}},\"description\":\"GPT Proto is a unified API aggregation platform connecting world-leading AI models such as Google, OpenAI, Claude, Midjourney, and more. With standardized integration and intelligent dispatching strategies, it offers cost-effective, scalable AI model access for developers, teams, and enterprises worldwide.\",\"articleSection\":\"Product Introduction\",\"keywords\":[\"AI Aggregation Platform\",\"Model API\",\"GPT Proto\",\"AI Routing\",\"OpenAI\",\"Claude\",\"Gemini\",\"Midjourney\"],\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://gptproto.com/\"}},{\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Why should businesses choose GPTProto over directly integrating with individual AI API providers like OpenAI or Anthropic?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Think of GPTProto as your universal API adapter for AI. If you integrate directly, you're managing separate API keys, billing cycles, and codebases for every new AI model that comes out. GPTProto unifies top-tier AI models—from Google and OpenAI to Midjourney and Claude—into a single interface. We handle the API format standardization (supporting official, OpenAI, and our own GPTProto formats), so your developers can switch from GPT-4 to Claude 3 with a simple config change, not a code rewrite. Plus, you get our volume-based AI discounts immediately.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How is GPTProto able to offer AI API pricing at roughly 60% of the official cost? Is this reliable?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"We get asked this a lot, and the answer lies in efficient AI resource management, not shortcuts. Our pricing model is built on 'Volume Pre-commitment' and 'Compute Pooling.' Essentially, we purchase massive quotas of enterprise-grade API compute globally and aggregate idle capacity from vetted sources. By routing your AI requests through this pooled infrastructure, we maximize efficiency and pass the bulk savings—often around 40% to 60% off official rates—directly to you. It's a logical commercial structure that allows our API to be cheaper without sacrificing quality.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"I see 'Talent Tech Global Limited' on the billing. Does a smaller entity have the API infrastructure to support large-scale enterprise AI traffic?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"We believe in full transparency here. Talent Tech Global Limited serves specifically as our billing and financial settlement entity to streamline global AI transactions. However, our technical backbone is a completely different beast. Our API infrastructure is distributed across major tech hubs like Silicon Valley, Singapore, and Hong Kong, utilizing a robust auto-scaling architecture. This means our capacity expands automatically to meet AI demand. Whether you are a startup or a listed company requiring massive concurrency, our API system handles the load with enterprise-grade stability.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"We have an AI project spanning the next 3 months and don't want to sign a long-term annual contract. What are our options?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"We completely understand that modern AI business is agile, and locking into a yearly contract doesn't always make sense. We've designed our model to lower your decision threshold. You can choose our 'Pay-as-you-go' API model for zero commitment—just top up and build. Alternatively, for slightly better planning without the handcuffs, we offer 'Quarterly Rolling Contracts.' This gives you the stability of a contract with the flexibility to adjust or pause as your AI project evolves.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is it better to manage multiple API keys from different AI providers or use a single, unified AI API platform?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"From an operational standpoint, a unified API platform is almost always superior. Managing multiple keys means multiple security vulnerabilities, fragmented billing, and 'spaghetti code' to handle different AI response formats. With GPTProto, you get one secure API key to access the world's best AI models (Llama, Flux, Gemini, etc.). It drastically reduces maintenance overhead and allows your team to focus on building AI features rather than fixing integrations.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How can I build a single AI application that leverages different models, like GPT-4 for text and Midjourney for images, using one API?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"This is exactly where GPTProto shines. Since we aggregate both LLMs (like GPT-4, Claude) and image generation AI models (like Midjourney, Flux, Ideogram), you don't need separate API pipelines. Your application can send a text prompt to GPT-4 via our API, receive the refined description, and immediately pipe that into Midjourney via the same API connection to generate an asset. It allows for seamless multi-modal AI workflows that would be a headache to build manually.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How does GPTProto ensure low latency and high availability when accessing multiple AI models via API?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Latency is the enemy of user experience, so we use an intelligent API scheduling strategy. Our system monitors the health and response times of underlying AI providers in real-time. If one path is congested, we route your request through optimized pathways to ensure the fastest possible delivery. For enterprise clients, we offer customized resource scheduling that prioritizes your AI traffic, ensuring that your app feels snappy even during peak hours.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What happens if a specific AI model provider (e.g., OpenAI) goes down? Does my API service stop?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"That's the beauty of using an AI aggregator. We support automatic failover for mainstream models. If a specific provider experiences an outage, our API system can be configured to switch your request to a comparable AI model (e.g., switching from GPT-4 to Claude 3 Opus) to keep your service running. This redundancy is a massive advantage for business continuity that you don't get with a direct, single-provider API integration.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How does GPTProto's 'Pay-as-you-go' API pricing compare to subscription AI models?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Subscription AI models often force you to pay for unused capacity or cap your potential during growth spurts. Our 'Pay-as-you-go' API model is strictly usage-based. You pay for the tokens or API calls you actually consume. For a growing AI application, this is usually much more cost-effective because your costs scale linearly with your revenue/users, rather than hitting you with a huge upfront fixed cost before you've earned it.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I use GPTProto if my existing code is already written for OpenAI's API?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Absolutely. We know AI migration can be painful, so we made it painless. GPTProto supports the standard OpenAI API format. In most cases, you simply need to change the 'Base URL' in your code to our endpoint and swap in your GPTProto API key. You can keep your existing logic while instantly gaining access to our lower rates and broader AI model selection.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How do business teams decide between AI models like GPT, Claude, and MidJourney for specific API use cases?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"It usually comes down to cost vs. capability. Because we provide a unified API interface, your business team can A/B test these AI models easily. For example, you might use GPT-4o for complex reasoning tasks, switch to Haiku or Gemini Flash for high-volume simple tasks to save money, and use Midjourney for high-fidelity creative visuals. GPTProto allows you to mix and match these based on real-world AI performance without needing engineering to rebuild the backend every time.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What measures are in place to ensure AI data security and prevent unauthorized API access?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Security is non-negotiable. We employ enterprise-grade encryption for data in transit and at rest. We do not store your AI payload data for training purposes. Additionally, our API keys come with granular controls, allowing you to set limits or rotate keys instantly if a breach is suspected. We act as a secure tunnel between you and the AI model providers, adding a layer of anonymity and protection to your corporate data.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How can organizations effectively transition from siloed AI systems to your integrated API platform?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Start small. You don't need to rip and replace everything day one. We recommend connecting one new feature or a non-critical AI service to GPTProto first. Once your developers see how easy it is to call Google, OpenAI, and DeepSeek from one API place—and your finance team sees the bill drop by 40%—scaling becomes a natural next step. Our support team is here to help architect that transition, ensuring your legacy AI systems aren't disrupted.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What specific metrics should businesses track to measure ROI when using a multi-model AI API platform?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Beyond just the obvious cost savings (which are significant with our discounts), you should track 'Time-to-Market' for new AI features and 'Engineering Hours Saved' on API maintenance. Because you aren't maintaining 10 different API libraries, your dev team moves faster. Also, track 'AI Model Performance vs. Cost'—since you can swap models easily, you can optimize your spend per user action much more aggressively than with a fixed provider.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Does GPTProto offer support for developers facing technical API integration issues with AI models?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, we aren't just a faceless API gateway. We provide comprehensive documentation for our three supported formats (Official, OpenAI, GPTProto). For our enterprise and business tier clients, we offer dedicated support channels to help troubleshoot integration logic, optimize prompt engineering across different AI models, and resolve any API latency concerns quickly. We succeed only when your product runs smoothly.\"}}]},{\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/inner/upload/2026/02/27/8b8fde27c36248c7a19f3e6c0e837ec4.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_600,m_lfit\",\"description\":\"The gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview/text-to-image model represents the cutting edge of rapid visual synthesis, specifically optimized for users who demand low latency without sacrificing prompt adherence. Hosted on the robust GPT Proto platform, gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview/text-to-image bridges the gap between conceptual ideation and high-fidelity output. By leveraging Google's most efficient visual architecture to date, gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview/text-to-image allows developers and creators to generate diverse artistic styles, realistic textures, and complex compositions in milliseconds. Whether you are building real-time interactive apps or batch-processing marketing assets, gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview/text-to-image on GPT Proto provides the stability and speed required for enterprise-level scaling.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"logo\":\"https://gptproto.com/favicon.ico\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":0.0404,\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\",\"priceValidUntil\":\"2027-03-20\",\"shippingDetails\":{\"@type\":\"OfferShippingDetails\",\"shippingRate\":{\"@type\":\"MonetaryAmount\",\"value\":0,\"currency\":\"USD\"},\"shippingDestination\":{\"@type\":\"DefinedRegion\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"deliveryTime\":{\"@type\":\"ShippingDeliveryTime\",\"handlingTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"},\"transitTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"}}},\"hasMerchantReturnPolicy\":{\"@type\":\"MerchantReturnPolicy\",\"applicableCountry\":\"US\",\"returnPolicyCategory\":\"https://schema.org/MerchantReturnNotPermitted\"}},\"review\":[{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Michael Chen\"},\"reviewBody\":\"GPTProto's pricing logic based on global compute pooling is sound. We get enterprise API rates without heavy upfront commitment.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Sarah Jenkins\"},\"reviewBody\":\"I worried about API infrastructure, but GPTProto's auto-scaling handled our traffic spikes perfectly.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"David Ross\"},\"reviewBody\":\"GPTProto's pay-as-you-go API model was a lifesaver. We validated our MVP without risky contracts.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Elena Rodriguez\"},\"reviewBody\":\"Integrating one API for Claude and GPT-4 via GPTProto saved us weeks. Zero maintenance overhead.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}}],\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"reviewCount\":15,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"gemini-3-pro-image-preview\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/12/15/592fe4d06e20497ab1903cf396073fd7.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_1192,m_lfit\",\"description\":\"The nano banana ai model represents a breakthrough in efficient machine learning, specifically designed for high-throughput environments where speed is paramount. By leveraging the nano banana ai API on GPTProto, businesses can deploy sophisticated intelligence without the overhead of massive infrastructure. The nano banana ai excels in natural language processing, sentiment analysis, and real-time data classification. Unlike bulky models, nano banana ai offers a streamlined architecture that reduces latency while maintaining high accuracy. With GPTProto's stable infrastructure, nano banana ai provides a reliable foundation for developers seeking to scale their AI-driven applications globally and cost-effectively through the specialized nano banana ai endpoint.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"logo\":\"https://gptproto.com/favicon.ico\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":0.0536,\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\",\"priceValidUntil\":\"2027-03-20\",\"shippingDetails\":{\"@type\":\"OfferShippingDetails\",\"shippingRate\":{\"@type\":\"MonetaryAmount\",\"value\":0,\"currency\":\"USD\"},\"shippingDestination\":{\"@type\":\"DefinedRegion\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"deliveryTime\":{\"@type\":\"ShippingDeliveryTime\",\"handlingTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"},\"transitTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"}}},\"hasMerchantReturnPolicy\":{\"@type\":\"MerchantReturnPolicy\",\"applicableCountry\":\"US\",\"returnPolicyCategory\":\"https://schema.org/MerchantReturnNotPermitted\"}},\"review\":[{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"James Foster\"},\"reviewBody\":\"We are seeing 60% savings on AI costs with GPTProto. This API makes us profitable this quarter.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Anita Patel\"},\"reviewBody\":\"Switching models on GPTProto requires no code changes. It gives our team total API agility.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Lucas Weber\"},\"reviewBody\":\"Piping text to Midjourney via GPTProto's unified API endpoints was incredibly simple.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Omar Farooq\"},\"reviewBody\":\"GPTProto's automatic API failover is brilliant. It keeps our application uptime at 99.9%.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}}],\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"reviewCount\":15,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"gemini-2.5-flash-image\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/12/35457b3477a642b094a3a4d9c979b8c7.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_800,m_lfit\",\"description\":\"Gemini 2.5 Flash Image, also known as Nano Banana, is Google’s advanced AI model for fast, high-quality image generation and editing. It supports blending multiple images, consistent character rendering, and precise natural language editing. The model leverages real-world knowledge for context-aware visuals, offers various aspect ratios. It is cost-effective and production-ready.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"logo\":\"https://gptproto.com/favicon.ico\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":0.0156,\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\",\"priceValidUntil\":\"2027-03-20\",\"shippingDetails\":{\"@type\":\"OfferShippingDetails\",\"shippingRate\":{\"@type\":\"MonetaryAmount\",\"value\":0,\"currency\":\"USD\"},\"shippingDestination\":{\"@type\":\"DefinedRegion\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"deliveryTime\":{\"@type\":\"ShippingDeliveryTime\",\"handlingTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"},\"transitTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"}}},\"hasMerchantReturnPolicy\":{\"@type\":\"MerchantReturnPolicy\",\"applicableCountry\":\"US\",\"returnPolicyCategory\":\"https://schema.org/MerchantReturnNotPermitted\"}},\"review\":[{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Kenji Sato\"},\"reviewBody\":\"GPTProto's smart API routing actually improves response times by picking the fastest nodes.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Rebecca Hughes\"},\"reviewBody\":\"GPTProto's enterprise API security protocols gave our compliance team total confidence.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Tomás Silva\"},\"reviewBody\":\"GPTProto let me consolidate all AI services into one dashboard, speeding up my shipping time.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Emily Zhao\"},\"reviewBody\":\"Running parallel API queries via GPTProto helps us reduce AI hallucination risks efficiently.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}}],\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"reviewCount\":15,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"gemini-2.5-flash-image-hd\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/28/3baca37798754adfa15dbe37b7d4137e.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_457,m_lfit\",\"description\":\"Gemini 2.5 Flash Image HD is an advanced AI image generation and editing model with enhanced resolution and creative control. It supports blending multiple images, maintaining character consistency, and precise local edits through natural language prompts. The model enables users to perform tasks like background blurring, object removal, pose alteration, and colorization with real-world understanding.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"logo\":\"https://gptproto.com/favicon.ico\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":0.02,\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\",\"priceValidUntil\":\"2027-03-20\",\"shippingDetails\":{\"@type\":\"OfferShippingDetails\",\"shippingRate\":{\"@type\":\"MonetaryAmount\",\"value\":0,\"currency\":\"USD\"},\"shippingDestination\":{\"@type\":\"DefinedRegion\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"deliveryTime\":{\"@type\":\"ShippingDeliveryTime\",\"handlingTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"},\"transitTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"}}},\"hasMerchantReturnPolicy\":{\"@type\":\"MerchantReturnPolicy\",\"applicableCountry\":\"US\",\"returnPolicyCategory\":\"https://schema.org/MerchantReturnNotPermitted\"}},\"review\":[{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Markus O’Connell\"},\"reviewBody\":\"Our ROI skyrocketed because we slashed API costs with GPTProto while reducing maintenance.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Sophie Dubois\"},\"reviewBody\":\"We manage global teams using different AI models through one GPTProto API billing account.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Alex Thorne\"},\"reviewBody\":\"GPTProto offers the perfect balance: enterprise API stability with flexible payments.\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"bestRating\":5}}],\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"reviewCount\":15,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"gpt-image-1.5\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/java/prod/de63e55c-1b45-4630-a1fb-d4e3c2a7f540.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_600,m_lfit\",\"description\":\"gpt-image-1.5/text-to-image is an advanced multimodal AI model built for accurate and fast text-to-image generation. Part of the GPT family, it leverages foundational GPT technology but is uniquely optimized for visual synthesis. Developers use it for rapid prototyping, creative design workflows, and automated image generation tasks. Compared to standard GPT models, it adds robust image processing, visual creativity, and seamless integration with multimodal workflows, making it a powerful tool for digital content creators, marketers, and product teams operating in diverse industries.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"logo\":\"https://gptproto.com/favicon.ico\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":4.8,\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\",\"priceValidUntil\":\"2027-03-20\",\"shippingDetails\":{\"@type\":\"OfferShippingDetails\",\"shippingRate\":{\"@type\":\"MonetaryAmount\",\"value\":0,\"currency\":\"USD\"},\"shippingDestination\":{\"@type\":\"DefinedRegion\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"deliveryTime\":{\"@type\":\"ShippingDeliveryTime\",\"handlingTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"},\"transitTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"}}},\"hasMerchantReturnPolicy\":{\"@type\":\"MerchantReturnPolicy\",\"applicableCountry\":\"US\",\"returnPolicyCategory\":\"https://schema.org/MerchantReturnNotPermitted\"},\"priceSpecification\":{\"@type\":\"UnitPriceSpecification\",\"price\":4.8,\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"referenceQuantity\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"value\":1000000,\"unitText\":\"tokens\"}}},\"review\":[],\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":5,\"reviewCount\":15,\"bestRating\":5}},{\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"gpt-image-1\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/12/53a7ec1b99c54a509f5df4fda42a4db6.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_800,m_lfit\",\"description\":\"The gpt-image-1/image-edit model represents a paradigm shift in visual manipulation. Unlike traditional diffusion-based editors, gpt-image-1/image-edit is a natively multimodal large language model. This means it doesn't just process pixels; it understands the semantic context of your requests. Whether you are adding a complex object to a scene or modifying lighting based on world knowledge, gpt-image-1/image-edit delivers unparalleled coherence. By integrating gpt-image-1/image-edit into your workflow on GPT Proto, you gain access to a tool that follows instructions with human-like reasoning, ensuring your visual edits are both creative and technically accurate.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"GPT Proto\",\"logo\":\"https://gptproto.com/favicon.ico\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":6,\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\",\"priceValidUntil\":\"2027-03-20\",\"shippingDetails\":{\"@type\":\"OfferShippingDetails\",\"shippingRate\":{\"@type\":\"MonetaryAmount\",\"value\":0,\"currency\":\"USD\"},\"shippingDestination\":{\"@type\":\"DefinedRegion\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"deliveryTime\":{\"@type\":\"ShippingDeliveryTime\",\"handlingTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"},\"transitTime\":{\"@type\":\"QuantitativeValue\",\"minValue\":0,\"maxValue\":1,\"unitCode\":\"DAY\"}}},\"hasMerchantReturnPolicy\":{