directly to the GPTProto API. Get scalable, pay-as-you-go access to our powerful model network.\",\"button\":{\"href\":\"https://gptproto.com/dashboard\",\"title\":\"Get API Access\"}},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/03/06/ee1037d7332a4641b00446921e5b6102.jpeg\",\"button\":{\"href\":\"https://editor.gptproto.com/\",\"title\":\"Start Creating\"},\"title\":\"All-in-One Creative Studio\",\"description\":\"Generate images and videos here. The GPTProto API ensures fast model updates and the lowest prices.\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/03/06/6f26304d3c084a6cbbcdd0570461e5bd.jpeg\",\"button\":{\"href\":\"https://gptproto.com/skills\",\"title\":\"Download Grace\"},\"title\":\"Grace: Desktop Automator\",\"description\":\"Grace handles all desktop operations and parallel tasks via GPTProto to drastically boost your efficiency.\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/03/06/e30d36530b09491ca99b32b2bc49614c.jpeg\",\"button\":{\"href\":\"https://docs.gptproto.com/docs/get-started/get-started/how-to-use/openclaw\",\"title\":\"View Tutorial\"},\"title\":\"Supercharged OpenClaw\",\"description\":\"Connect OpenClaw to GPTProto API for smart routing, massive model selection, and much lower costs.\"}]},\"latestVideoModels\":{\"title\":\"State-of-the-Art Video Generation via GPTProto API\",\"description\":\"Integrate the world's most advanced video AI models instantly with GPTProto. We aggregate Sora, Google Veo, Kling-Video, Hailuo, Wan, and Seedance into one developer-friendly GPTProto API endpoint. Experience the latest in high-frame-rate, coherent video AI synthesis without technical fragmentation.\",\"models\":[\"veo3.1-fast\",\"veo3.1-pro\",\"sora-2\",\"sora-2-pro\",\"kling-v3.0-pro\",\"kling-video-o1-pro\",\"wan-2.6\",\"viduq3-pro\",\"viduq2-pro\",\"seedance-1-5-pro-251215\",\"hailuo-2.3-pro\",\"hailuo-02-pro\"]},\"universalConnection\":{\"title\":\"GPTProto API — Unified Access with Intelligent Reliability\",\"description\":\"Unlike typical AI platforms that lock you into single providers, GPTProto offers a unified API that connects you to every top-tier model in one seamless integration. GPTProto intelligently routes API requests for the best cost-speed balance, guarantees zero downtime with automatic failover, and ensures full data privacy.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Explore Models\",\"link\":\"https://gptproto.com/model\"},\"content\":[{\"title\":\"Universal Connection via GPTProto\",\"description\":\"Plug into GPTProto once and unlock every top-tier model instantly. Our API plays perfectly with standard SDKs, so you don't have to rewrite code to access global AI capabilities.\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/01/26/94c692133d574518872f32f9d36dd2dc.JPEG\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Browse all\",\"href\":\"https://gptproto.com/model\"}},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/01/26/426ed0de7cca4dfcbd241086496a8a59.JPEG\",\"title\":\"Zero Downtime API\",\"description\":\"Don't let provider outages crash your app. GPTProto automatically reroutes your API request to a working backup model if the primary source fails, ensuring rock-solid stability.\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"href\":\"https://gptproto.com/news/gemini-uptime-reliability-guide\"}},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/01/26/678bec6a303949938b5351083b3d451d.JPEG\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"href\":\"https://gptproto.com/news/ai-provider-routing-llama\"},\"title\":\"Smart Cost \u0026 Speed\",\"description\":\"Get the lowest prices without the lag. GPTProto optimizes the API routing behind the scenes to ensure you receive the fastest response times at the best possible rates.\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/01/26/7137411a555e49a1aa786b022d202ecf.JPEG\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"href\":\"https://gptproto.com/news/ai-data-privacy-policy\"},\"title\":\"Secure API Data Privacy\",\"description\":\"GPTProto gives you full control. You decide exactly which providers are allowed to touch your data through our API, ensuring compliance and peace of mind.\"}]},\"latestImageModels\":{\"title\":\"All-in-One AI Art Generator via GPTProto API\",\"description\":\"Empower your applications with GPTProto's versatile image API engine. From the photorealism of Flux and Midjourney to the creative precision of Kling-Image and GPT-Image, GPTProto provides a stable, standardized API for every visual AI need.\",\"models\":[\"gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview\",\"gemini-3-pro-image-preview\",\"gemini-2.5-flash-image\",\"gemini-2.5-flash-image-hd\",\"gpt-image-1.5\",\"gpt-image-1\",\"kling-image-o1\",\"seedream-5-0-260128\"]},\"integrations\":{\"title\":\"One GPTProto Platform, Endless API Possibilities\",\"description\":\"Whether you need a raw API for enterprise integration or a ready-made tool for creative work, GPTProto adapts to your needs. Explore flexible solutions designed for technical teams and creators, all powered by the GPTProto network.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Explore Models\",\"link\":\"https://gptproto.com/model\"},\"content\":[{\"title\":\"Enterprise API Integration\",\"description\":\"Empower your tech team by integrating the GPTProto API directly into business workflows. Leverage GPTProto's full model capabilities with a scalable, pay-as-you-go structure.\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/02/28/36d48204760a4938922e80e88feff79d.jpeg\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Get API Access\",\"href\":\"https://gptproto.com/dashboard\"}},{\"title\":\"AI Image Studio (No Code)\",\"description\":\"Access GPTProto's powerful image generation models through our visual editor. No coding required—just simple, pay-per-use creativity powered by the GPTProto API.\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/02/28/98afec99da354b12a1937027128ca1c0.jpeg\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Start Creating\",\"href\":\"https://editor.gptproto.com/\"}},{\"title\":\"Grace: Desktop Agent by GPTProto\",\"description\":\"Automate coding and complex tasks with Grace. Grace utilizes the GPTProto API to bring the power of ClaudeCode and other models directly to your desktop environment securely.\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/02/28/db0f39b54b5d4aa09896b0320b1a5876.jpeg\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Download Grace\",\"href\":\"https://gptproto.com/skills\"}},{\"title\":\"Build Your Own OpenClaw\",\"description\":\"Create custom intelligent agents using the GPTProto API. We provide tutorials to help you build your own OpenClaw, enjoying GPTProto's low discount rates and full control.\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/02/28/1b61f3e99035448391f2db23e00272aa.jpeg\",\"button\":{\"href\":\"https://docs.gptproto.com/docs/get-started/get-started/how-to-use/openclaw\",\"title\":\"View Tutorial\"}}]},\"pricing\":{\"title\":\"Flexible GPTProto API Pricing – Simplified for Business\",\"description\":\"GPTProto offers transparent pricing to fit your AI needs. With our clear 3-month short-term plans, you can access the GPTProto API without annual lock-ins. Enjoy flexible commitments, no rate limits, and streamlined integration across multiple models using a single GPTProto account.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Get Started Now\",\"link\":\"https://gptproto.com/dashboard/billing-center\"},\"content\":[{\"title\":\"Entry Tier – Self‑Service API Access\",\"description\":\"Perfect for startups, the Entry Tier offers full GPTProto API access for under $10k/month. Get standard discounts and immediate scalability with GPTProto.\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/01/26/123233cbfc6c4f38a1075053ee26aa8a.jpeg\"},{\"title\":\"Business Tier – High Volume API Discounts\",\"description\":\"For teams spending 10k–50k/month, the GPTProto Business Tier provides dedicated support and higher API discount rates to keep your projects agile.\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/01/26/e5370960ad8440e6bec215cf9797c6fb.jpeg\"},{\"title\":\"Enterprise Tier – Custom API Solutions\",\"description\":\"Spending over $50k/month? GPTProto offers tailored agreements, compliance support, and No Rate Limit policies for massive API concurrency.\",\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/01/26/9031ca9b5ea743c68feeeeba5f21cb24.jpeg\"}]},\"llm\":{\"title\":\"Leading Text \u0026 Audio Models via GPTProto API\",\"description\":\"Discover advanced AI tools for text and audio through GPTProto. Our API helps writers and developers generate realistic speech, compose AI music, and craft engaging stories using the latest models on the GPTProto platform.\",\"models\":[\"gpt-5.4\",\"gpt-5.4-nano\",\"gpt-5.4-mini\",\"gpt-5.3-codex\",\"gemini-3.1-pro-preview\",\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"kimi-k2.5\",\"glm-5\",\"gpt-5.2\",\"gemini-3-pro-preview\",\"gpt-5.1\",\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\"]},\"customerReviews\":{\"title\":\"Trusted by the Community: Real GPTProto API User Stories\",\"description\":\"See why developers are switching to GPTProto for their API needs. From competitive pricing to superior model responsiveness, read authentic feedback about the GPTProto platform.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Start Using GPTProto Today\",\"link\":\"https://gptproto.com/dashboard/billing-center\"},\"content\":[{\"avatar\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/02/28/8c05951154634ed5ba99ea5e6cec2612.jpeg\",\"name\":\"Switching for Better API Pricing\",\"feedback\":\"A developer highlights GPTProto's competitive pricing and confirms that the GPTProto API is extremely responsive with zero integration issues.\"},{\"name\":\"Top-Tier Model Quality with GPTProto\",\"avatar\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/02/28/647e506440ed47a7837e16c5dad8e7e0.jpeg\",\"feedback\":\"A loyal user relies on GPTProto for roleplaying via Janitor, citing high satisfaction with the API model quality and platform reliability.\"},{\"name\":\"GPTProto: Unbeatable API Value\",\"avatar\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/02/28/a2749a705a264aebabff5eca3ff3b6d2.jpeg\",\"feedback\":\"Initially skeptical of the deep discounts, this user became a fan after a trial, proving GPTProto delivers genuine value and reliable API access.\"}]},\"discount\":{\"title\":\"Enterprise-Grade Performance via GPTProto Global API Compute Pooling\",\"description\":\"GPTProto aggregates underutilized enterprise AI compute quotas globally. By monetizing idle capacity, GPTProto delivers tier-1 API reliability at a fraction of market rates, ensuring 95% TTFB within 20s while lowering your AI infrastructure costs.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Contact us\",\"link\":\"mailto:gptproto.official@gmail.com\"},\"content\":[{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/20/c5410080ef0a4da1bcfb1d793c104f5f.png\",\"title\":\"Gemini AI API Price: 60–80% Off\",\"description\":\"Access gemini-2.5-pro, gemini-2.5-flash, and other models via GPTProto at significantly reduced API rates.\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/20/fb5e32888ab94c58b7db6ce4fb3114f4.png\",\"title\":\"Claude AI API Price: 50–80% Off\",\"description\":\"Get Claude Opus 4.5 and Claude Sonnet 4.5 through the GPTProto API for less.\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/20/774f217ca6da42fa92e6bdc652542e5e.png\",\"title\":\"GPT AI API Price: 40–70% Off\",\"description\":\"Use gpt-5.2, gpt-5.1-codex-max, and more via GPTProto with massive API discounts.\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/20/8dbefd0373384f5dbd562fada70d236a.png\",\"title\":\"Grok AI API Price: 40–50% Off\",\"description\":\"Integrate grok-4-1-fast-reasoning and other generative AI options using the GPTProto API.\"}]},\"solution\":{\"title\":\"Tailored GPTProto API Solutions for Teams\",\"description\":\"From solo hackers to enterprises, the GPTProto unified API accelerates development and simplifies cloud spend. GPTProto ensures scalable stability for all your mission-critical AI applications.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Get Started Now\",\"link\":\"https://gptproto.com/dashboard\"},\"content\":[{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/17/4734aa47044f4d939207c10429158a2f.jpeg\",\"description\":\"I need to quickly produce high-quality media using powerful AI generation APIs on GPTProto.\",\"title\":\"Creative AI Media Makers\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Start Creating\",\"href\":\"https://gptproto.com/model\"}},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/17/3bdeed679d4e41ff98b6e31efaba63bc.png\",\"description\":\"I need an API Key to connect GPTProto to my favorite AI agent app for better conversations.\",\"title\":\"Personal AI Agent Users\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Read Guide\",\"href\":\"https://docs.gptproto.com/docs/guide/ai-chat\"}},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/17/f2ceac1680d7459682cf988ee169a29d.png\",\"description\":\"I'm integrating the GPTProto API into tools like Claude Code to enhance development efficiency.\",\"title\":\"AI-Powered Code Developers\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Read Guide\",\"href\":\"https://docs.gptproto.com/docs/guide/claude-code\"}},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/17/40f677a62c184e9a9b5680e810d7039f.png\",\"description\":\"Our business systems directly call the GPTProto API to automate workflows and deliver AI services.\",\"title\":\"Enterprise GPTProto API Clients\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"View Docs\",\"href\":\"https://docs.gptproto.com/docs/api/openai/gpt-4.1/official-format(chat)/text-to-text\"}}]},\"howToUse\":{\"title\":\"Your Gateway to All Top AI Models – GPTProto API Setup\",\"description\":\"Experience the power of the unified GPTProto API interface. From account creation to your first API call, GPTProto streamlines the process, giving you immediate access to reliable AI resources.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Get Started Now\",\"link\":\"https://gptproto.com/dashboard\"},\"content\":[{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/10/27/41e1ab0f6c284fadb9dab46264e3782f.png\",\"description\":\"Sign up with your email to begin managing your AI services on GPTProto.\",\"title\":\"Create a GPTProto Account\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/10/27/05fd0a3b0f484f3281a8f178a09e3772.png\",\"description\":\"Top up your account balance to use across any supported AI model via the GPTProto API.\",\"title\":\"Add API Balance\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/10/27/c6953dad3f634c4e9fad9fb78b66c32e.png\",\"description\":\"Generate your unified API key from the GPTProto dashboard to start authenticating requests.\",\"title\":\"Get Your API Key\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/10/27/65013365d20f4e558a18b8d20dea2963.png\",\"description\":\"Use your GPTProto API key for seamless AI calls and build innovative solutions.\",\"title\":\"Send First API Request\"}]},\"whyChoose\":{\"title\":\"Streamline Your AI Integration with the GPTProto API Gateway\",\"description\":\"Stop juggling multiple accounts. Access 200+ top AI models through the GPTProto standardized API interface. Enjoy enterprise-grade stability and save up to 40% with GPTProto compared to direct AI providers.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Get Started Now\",\"link\":\"https://gptproto.com/dashboard\"},\"content\":[{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/01/14/f95c238747924d67bcff92bebf1760a4.jpeg\",\"description\":\"GPTProto utilizes intelligent API scheduling strategies to monitor model health. If a provider fails, the GPTProto API automatically reroutes requests to a backup, ensuring consistent high-availability service.\",\"title\":\"Rock-Solid Stability with GPTProto\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/01/14/1ae53f36b883487b9298e9bf2ab0fcaf.jpeg\",\"description\":\"GPTProto passes significant API savings to you through volume aggregation. Access models at ~60% of official costs with our dashboard, giving you precise control over your GPTProto API budget.\",\"title\":\"Premium Models, Wholesale Prices via GPTProto\"},{\"image\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/17/d791a615dd124e24b9bc003c5a79d362.jpg\",\"description\":\"GPTProto normalizes responses into a standardized API format. Switch between text, image, and video models simply by changing parameters in the GPTProto API, making integration maintenance-free.\",\"title\":\"Code Once with GPTProto API\"}]},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"GPTProto FAQ: Unified API and Multi-Model Integration\",\"description\":\"Core Questions about the GPTProto AI API Aggregation Platform\",\"content\":[{\"question\":\"Why choose GPTProto over direct AI API providers?\",\"answer\":\"GPTProto acts as your universal API adapter. Instead of managing separate keys for every provider, GPTProto unifies top models like Google and OpenAI into a single interface. We standardize the API format, so switching from GPT-4 to Claude is just a config change on GPTProto, not a rewrite.\"},{\"question\":\"How does GPTProto offer such low API prices?\",\"answer\":\"GPTProto achieves low pricing through 'Compute Pooling'. We aggregate massive global enterprise API quotas and idle capacity. By routing requests through the GPTProto infrastructure, we pass savings of 40-60% directly to you without sacrificing quality.\"},{\"question\":\"Does GPTProto have the infrastructure for enterprise API traffic?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. While 'Talent Tech Global' handles billing, the GPTProto API infrastructure is distributed across major tech hubs with robust auto-scaling. GPTProto handles massive concurrency with enterprise-grade stability for startups and listed companies alike.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use GPTProto without a long-term contract?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. GPTProto offers a 'Pay-as-you-go' API model for zero commitment. For better planning, GPTProto also provides 'Quarterly Rolling Contracts', offering stability without the handcuffs of annual agreements.\"},{\"question\":\"Is one unified GPTProto API better than multiple keys?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Managing multiple keys creates security risks and 'spaghetti code'. With GPTProto, you get one secure API key to access all models. GPTProto reduces maintenance overhead, letting your team focus on building features.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I build multi-modal apps using the GPTProto API?\",\"answer\":\"Exactly. GPTProto aggregates LLMs and image models in one place. You can pipe text from GPT-4 into Midjourney via the same GPTProto API connection, creating seamless workflows that are difficult to build manually.\"},{\"question\":\"How does GPTProto ensure low API latency?\",\"answer\":\"GPTProto uses intelligent API scheduling. We monitor provider health in real-time. If a path is congested, GPTProto routes your request through optimized pathways to ensure the fastest delivery.\"},{\"question\":\"What if an AI provider goes down? Does GPTProto stop?\",\"answer\":\"No. GPTProto supports automatic failover. If a provider fails, the GPTProto API switches to a comparable model to keep your service running, offering business continuity you don't get with direct integration.\"},{\"question\":\"How does GPTProto's pay-as-you-go compare to subscriptions?\",\"answer\":\"GPTProto's 'Pay-as-you-go' API model is strictly usage-based. You pay only for what you consume. This makes GPTProto more cost-effective for growing apps compared to fixed subscriptions.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I use GPTProto with existing OpenAI-compatible code?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. GPTProto supports the standard OpenAI API format. Just change the 'Base URL' to the GPTProto endpoint and swap in your GPTProto API key to instantly access lower rates.\"},{\"question\":\"How do I choose between models on GPTProto?\",\"answer\":\"With GPTProto, you can A/B test models easily. Use GPT-4o for reasoning and Gemini Flash for speed via the same API. GPTProto allows you to mix and match based on performance without rebuilding your backend.\"},{\"question\":\"Is my data secure with the GPTProto API?\",\"answer\":\"Security is paramount at GPTProto. We use enterprise-grade encryption and do not store API payload data for training. GPTProto acts as a secure tunnel, adding a layer of privacy to your corporate data.\"},{\"question\":\"How do I transition to the GPTProto API platform?\",\"answer\":\"Start small. Connect one feature to GPTProto. Once developers see the ease of the GPTProto API and finance sees the savings, scaling is natural. Our support team helps architect your transition to GPTProto.\"},{\"question\":\"What ROI metrics should I track with GPTProto?\",\"answer\":\"Track cost savings, 'Time-to-Market', and engineering hours saved. Because GPTProto simplifies integration, your team moves faster. Also, track model performance vs. cost optimization enabled by GPTProto.\"},{\"question\":\"Does GPTProto offer developer support?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. GPTProto provides comprehensive documentation and dedicated support channels for business clients. We help optimize integration logic and resolve API latency issues to ensure your product runs smoothly on GPTProto.\"}]},\"comment\":{\"title\":\"Trusted by Developers to Scale Innovation via GPTProto API\",\"description\":\"Real experiences from diverse industries using the GPTProto AI API platform.\",\"content\":[{\"comment\":\"GPTProto's pricing logic based on global compute pooling is sound. We get enterprise API rates without heavy upfront commitment.\",\"userName\":\"Michael Chen\",\"job\":\"VP of Engineering\"},{\"comment\":\"I worried about API infrastructure, but GPTProto's auto-scaling handled our traffic spikes perfectly.\",\"userName\":\"Sarah Jenkins\",\"job\":\"CTO\"},{\"comment\":\"GPTProto's pay-as-you-go API model was a lifesaver. We validated our MVP without risky contracts.\",\"userName\":\"David Ross\",\"job\":\"Startup Founder\"},{\"comment\":\"Integrating one API for Claude and GPT-4 via GPTProto saved us weeks. Zero maintenance overhead.\",\"userName\":\"Elena Rodriguez\",\"job\":\"Lead Developer\"},{\"comment\":\"We are seeing 60% savings on AI costs with GPTProto. This API makes us profitable this quarter.\",\"userName\":\"James Foster\",\"job\":\"Head of Operations\"},{\"comment\":\"Switching models on GPTProto requires no code changes. It gives our team total API agility.\",\"userName\":\"Anita Patel\",\"job\":\"Product Manager\"},{\"comment\":\"Piping text to Midjourney via GPTProto's unified API endpoints was incredibly simple.\",\"userName\":\"Lucas Weber\",\"job\":\"Creative Tech Lead\"},{\"comment\":\"GPTProto's automatic API failover is brilliant. It keeps our application uptime at 99.9%.\",\"userName\":\"Omar Farooq\",\"job\":\"DevOps Manager\"},{\"comment\":\"GPTProto's smart API routing actually improves response times by picking the fastest nodes.\",\"userName\":\"Kenji Sato\",\"job\":\"Senior Architect\"},{\"comment\":\"GPTProto's enterprise API security protocols gave our compliance team total confidence.\",\"userName\":\"Rebecca Hughes\",\"job\":\"CIO\"},{\"comment\":\"GPTProto let me consolidate all AI services into one dashboard, speeding up my shipping time.\",\"userName\":\"Tomás Silva\",\"job\":\"Indie Developer\"},{\"comment\":\"Running parallel API queries via GPTProto helps us reduce AI hallucination risks efficiently.\",\"userName\":\"Emily Zhao\",\"job\":\"Data Scientist\"},{\"comment\":\"Our ROI skyrocketed because we slashed API costs with GPTProto while reducing maintenance.\",\"userName\":\"Markus O’Connell\",\"job\":\"Finance Director\"},{\"comment\":\"We manage global teams using different AI models through one GPTProto API billing account.\",\"userName\":\"Sophie Dubois\",\"job\":\"Global IT Director\"},{\"comment\":\"GPTProto offers the perfect balance: enterprise API stability with flexible payments.\",\"userName\":\"Alex Thorne\",\"job\":\"Co-founder \u0026 CEO\"}]}},\"latestImageModels\":[{\"isLockPrice\":true,\"model\":\"gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview\",\"manufacturerCode\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerName\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerIcon\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/AiIcon/Gemini.png\",\"officialBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"74740000\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.101\",\"inPrice\":\"0\",\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":\"0\",\"outPriceStr\":null},\"platformBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"2.9896E+7\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.0404\",\"inPrice\":null,\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":null,\"outPriceStr\":null,\"discountRate\":\"60% off\",\"discountRateNum\":\"0.4\"},\"scenarios\":null,\"modelTag\":[\"text-to-image\",\"image-edit\"],\"inputTag\":null,\"outputTag\":null,\"apiUrl\":null,\"meta\":\"\",\"metaDescription\":\"The gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview/text-to-image model represents the cutting edge of rapid visual synthesis, specifically optimized for users who demand low latency without sacrificing prompt adherence. Hosted on the robust GPT Proto platform, gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview/text-to-image bridges the gap between conceptual ideation and high-fidelity output. By leveraging Google's most efficient visual architecture to date, gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview/text-to-image allows developers and creators to generate diverse artistic styles, realistic textures, and complex compositions in milliseconds. Whether you are building real-time interactive apps or batch-processing marketing assets, gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview/text-to-image on GPT Proto provides the stability and speed required for enterprise-level scaling.\",\"extPriceModelConfig\":null,\"mediaUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/inner/upload/2026/02/27/8b8fde27c36248c7a19f3e6c0e837ec4.jpeg\",\"thumbUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/inner/upload/2026/02/27/8b8fde27c36248c7a19f3e6c0e837ec4.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_600,m_lfit\",\"scene\":\"image-edit\"},{\"isLockPrice\":true,\"model\":\"gemini-3-pro-image-preview\",\"manufacturerCode\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerName\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerIcon\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/AiIcon/Gemini.png\",\"officialBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"99160000\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.134\",\"inPrice\":\"0\",\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":\"0\",\"outPriceStr\":null},\"platformBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"3.9664E+7\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.0536\",\"inPrice\":null,\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":null,\"outPriceStr\":null,\"discountRate\":\"60% off\",\"discountRateNum\":\"0.4\"},\"scenarios\":null,\"modelTag\":[\"text-to-image\",\"image-edit\"],\"inputTag\":null,\"outputTag\":null,\"apiUrl\":null,\"meta\":\"\",\"metaDescription\":\"The nano banana ai model represents a breakthrough in efficient machine learning, specifically designed for high-throughput environments where speed is paramount. By leveraging the nano banana ai API on GPTProto, businesses can deploy sophisticated intelligence without the overhead of massive infrastructure. The nano banana ai excels in natural language processing, sentiment analysis, and real-time data classification. Unlike bulky models, nano banana ai offers a streamlined architecture that reduces latency while maintaining high accuracy. With GPTProto's stable infrastructure, nano banana ai provides a reliable foundation for developers seeking to scale their AI-driven applications globally and cost-effectively through the specialized nano banana ai endpoint.\",\"extPriceModelConfig\":null,\"mediaUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/12/15/592fe4d06e20497ab1903cf396073fd7.jpeg\",\"thumbUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/12/15/592fe4d06e20497ab1903cf396073fd7.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_1192,m_lfit\",\"scene\":\"image-edit\"},{\"isLockPrice\":true,\"model\":\"gemini-2.5-flash-image\",\"manufacturerCode\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerName\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerIcon\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/AiIcon/Gemini.png\",\"officialBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"28860000\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.039\",\"inPrice\":\"0\",\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":\"0\",\"outPriceStr\":null},\"platformBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"1.1544E+7\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.0156\",\"inPrice\":null,\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":null,\"outPriceStr\":null,\"discountRate\":\"60% off\",\"discountRateNum\":\"0.4\"},\"scenarios\":\"\u003cp\u003eGemini-2.5-Flash image is a cutting-edge, high-performance visual representation designed for rapid deployment, featuring enhanced AI capabilities and seamless integration for advanced data processing.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"modelTag\":[\"text-to-image\",\"image-edit\"],\"inputTag\":null,\"outputTag\":null,\"apiUrl\":\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/models#gemini-2.5-flash-image-preview\",\"meta\":\"\",\"metaDescription\":\"Gemini 2.5 Flash Image, also known as Nano Banana, is Google’s advanced AI model for fast, high-quality image generation and editing. It supports blending multiple images, consistent character rendering, and precise natural language editing. The model leverages real-world knowledge for context-aware visuals, offers various aspect ratios. It is cost-effective and production-ready.\",\"extPriceModelConfig\":null,\"mediaUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/12/35457b3477a642b094a3a4d9c979b8c7.png\",\"thumbUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/12/35457b3477a642b094a3a4d9c979b8c7.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_800,m_lfit\",\"scene\":\"image-edit\"},{\"isLockPrice\":true,\"model\":\"gemini-2.5-flash-image-hd\",\"manufacturerCode\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerName\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerIcon\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/AiIcon/Gemini.png\",\"officialBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"37000000\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.05\",\"inPrice\":\"0\",\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":\"0\",\"outPriceStr\":null},\"platformBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"1.48E+7\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.02\",\"inPrice\":null,\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":null,\"outPriceStr\":null,\"discountRate\":\"60% off\",\"discountRateNum\":\"0.4\"},\"scenarios\":\"\u003cp\u003eAn advanced AI model designed for fast, high-definition image generation. It balances quality and speed, enabling realistic visuals with rich detail in minimal time. Trained on diverse datasets, it supports design mockups, marketing content, and creative artwork. It\u0026rsquo;s optimized for delivering stunning HD images with efficient inference performance for professionals.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"modelTag\":[\"text-to-image\",\"image-edit\"],\"inputTag\":null,\"outputTag\":null,\"apiUrl\":null,\"meta\":\"\",\"metaDescription\":\"Gemini 2.5 Flash Image HD is an advanced AI image generation and editing model with enhanced resolution and creative control. It supports blending multiple images, maintaining character consistency, and precise local edits through natural language prompts. The model enables users to perform tasks like background blurring, object removal, pose alteration, and colorization with real-world understanding.\",\"extPriceModelConfig\":null,\"mediaUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/28/3baca37798754adfa15dbe37b7d4137e.jpeg\",\"thumbUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/28/3baca37798754adfa15dbe37b7d4137e.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_457,m_lfit\",\"scene\":\"image-edit\"},{\"isLockPrice\":false,\"model\":\"gpt-image-1.5\",\"manufacturerCode\":\"OpenAI\",\"manufacturerName\":\"OpenAI\",\"manufacturerIcon\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/AiIcon/GPT.png\",\"officialBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"-1\",\"lockPriceStr\":null,\"inPrice\":\"5920\",\"inPriceStr\":\"8\",\"outPrice\":\"23680\",\"outPriceStr\":\"32\"},\"platformBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":null,\"lockPriceStr\":null,\"inPrice\":\"3552.0\",\"inPriceStr\":\"4.8\",\"outPrice\":\"14208.0\",\"outPriceStr\":\"19.2\",\"discountRate\":\"40% off\",\"discountRateNum\":\"0.6\"},\"scenarios\":null,\"modelTag\":[\"text-to-image\",\"image-edit\"],\"inputTag\":null,\"outputTag\":null,\"apiUrl\":null,\"meta\":\"\",\"metaDescription\":\"gpt-image-1.5/text-to-image is an advanced multimodal AI model built for accurate and fast text-to-image generation. Part of the GPT family, it leverages foundational GPT technology but is uniquely optimized for visual synthesis. Developers use it for rapid prototyping, creative design workflows, and automated image generation tasks. Compared to standard GPT models, it adds robust image processing, visual creativity, and seamless integration with multimodal workflows, making it a powerful tool for digital content creators, marketers, and product teams operating in diverse industries.\",\"extPriceModelConfig\":\"\",\"mediaUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/java/prod/de63e55c-1b45-4630-a1fb-d4e3c2a7f540.png\",\"thumbUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/java/prod/de63e55c-1b45-4630-a1fb-d4e3c2a7f540.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_600,m_lfit\",\"scene\":\"text-to-image\"},{\"isLockPrice\":false,\"model\":\"gpt-image-1\",\"manufacturerCode\":\"OpenAI\",\"manufacturerName\":\"OpenAI\",\"manufacturerIcon\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/AiIcon/GPT.png\",\"officialBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"-1\",\"lockPriceStr\":null,\"inPrice\":\"7400\",\"inPriceStr\":\"10\",\"outPrice\":\"29600\",\"outPriceStr\":\"40\"},\"platformBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":null,\"lockPriceStr\":null,\"inPrice\":\"4440.0\",\"inPriceStr\":\"6\",\"outPrice\":\"17760.0\",\"outPriceStr\":\"24\",\"discountRate\":\"40% off\",\"discountRateNum\":\"0.6\"},\"scenarios\":\"\u003col\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003e1.From Sketch to UI Mockup: Designers submit rough sketches and the model generates usable UI mockups.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\u003c/li\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003e2.Smart Ad Redesign: Upload an old ad image and the model re-layouts it with the new copy and style.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\u003c/li\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003e3.Style Transfer for Art: Artists convert photos into Picasso-style illustrations for NFT projects.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\u003c/li\u003e\\n\u003c/ol\u003e\",\"modelTag\":[\"image-edit\",\"text-to-image\"],\"inputTag\":null,\"outputTag\":null,\"apiUrl\":\"https://platform.openai.com/docs/models/gpt-image-1\",\"meta\":\"\",\"metaDescription\":\"The gpt-image-1/image-edit model represents a paradigm shift in visual manipulation. Unlike traditional diffusion-based editors, gpt-image-1/image-edit is a natively multimodal large language model. This means it doesn't just process pixels; it understands the semantic context of your requests. Whether you are adding a complex object to a scene or modifying lighting based on world knowledge, gpt-image-1/image-edit delivers unparalleled coherence. By integrating gpt-image-1/image-edit into your workflow on GPT Proto, you gain access to a tool that follows instructions with human-like reasoning, ensuring your visual edits are both creative and technically accurate.\",\"extPriceModelConfig\":\"\",\"mediaUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/12/53a7ec1b99c54a509f5df4fda42a4db6.png\",\"thumbUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/12/53a7ec1b99c54a509f5df4fda42a4db6.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_800,m_lfit\",\"scene\":\"image-edit\"},{\"isLockPrice\":true,\"model\":\"kling-image-o1\",\"manufacturerCode\":\"Kling\",\"manufacturerName\":\"Kling\",\"manufacturerIcon\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/AiIcon/Kling.png\",\"officialBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"20720000.000\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.028\",\"inPrice\":\"0\",\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":\"0\",\"outPriceStr\":null},\"platformBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"16576000.0000\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.0224\",\"inPrice\":null,\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":null,\"outPriceStr\":null,\"discountRate\":\"20% off\",\"discountRateNum\":\"0.8\"},\"scenarios\":null,\"modelTag\":[\"text-to-image\",\"image-to-image\"],\"inputTag\":null,\"outputTag\":null,\"apiUrl\":null,\"meta\":\"\",\"metaDescription\":\"kling-image-o1/text-to-image is a state of the art generative model within the Kling AI ecosystem designed for high precision visual synthesis. As an evolution of the standard Kling image series, this o1 variant introduces enhanced reasoning capabilities for better semantic understanding of complex prompts. It excels at creating photorealistic textures, cinematic lighting, and intricate architectural details that standard models often miss. Whether you are generating assets for digital entertainment or high end marketing collateral, kling-image-o1/text-to-image provides a robust, professional grade output. Its core strength lies in its ability to maintain spatial consistency and aesthetic harmony, making it a leading choice for developers seeking reliable image generation through the GPT Proto platform.\",\"extPriceModelConfig\":\"$19\",\"mediaUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/inner/upload/2026/01/13/a2c7e15c99f047e38f212560c135de51.png\",\"thumbUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/inner/upload/2026/01/13/a2c7e15c99f047e38f212560c135de51.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_600,m_lfit\",\"scene\":\"image-to-image\"},{\"isLockPrice\":true,\"model\":\"seedream-5-0-260128\",\"manufacturerCode\":\"Doubao\",\"manufacturerName\":\"Bytedance\",\"manufacturerIcon\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/2025/11/20/c9c08eaa968f43dc94f49ce41e6992b2.png\",\"officialBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"25900000\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.035\",\"inPrice\":\"0\",\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":\"0\",\"outPriceStr\":null},\"platformBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"2.2015E+7\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.0298\",\"inPrice\":null,\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":null,\"outPriceStr\":null,\"discountRate\":\"15% off\",\"discountRateNum\":\"0.85\"},\"scenarios\":null,\"modelTag\":[\"text-to-image\",\"image-edit\"],\"inputTag\":null,\"outputTag\":null,\"apiUrl\":null,\"meta\":\"\",\"metaDescription\":\"The seedream-5-0-260128/text-to-image model represents a significant leap in the evolution of visual synthesis. Engineered for precision and aesthetic nuance, seedream-5-0-260128/text-to-image excels at interpreting complex prompts into hyper-realistic or stylistically specific imagery. Available through the GPT Proto infrastructure, it offers developers and creative directors a stable, scalable environment for high-volume asset production. Whether you are generating marketing collateral or conceptualizing architectural designs, seedream-5-0-260128/text-to-image provides the consistency and detail necessary for professional-grade output without the common artifacts found in lower-tier models.\",\"extPriceModelConfig\":null,\"mediaUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/inner/upload/2026/02/24/66040d073d564fb9815bbafb8e9f35c1.jpeg\",\"thumbUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/inner/upload/2026/02/24/66040d073d564fb9815bbafb8e9f35c1.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800,h_600,m_lfit\",\"scene\":\"text-to-image\"}],\"latestVideoModels\":[{\"isLockPrice\":true,\"model\":\"veo3.1-fast\",\"manufacturerCode\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerName\":\"Google\",\"manufacturerIcon\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/ai-draw/AiIcon/Gemini.png\",\"officialBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"370000000\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.5\",\"inPrice\":\"0\",\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":\"0\",\"outPriceStr\":null},\"platformBasePrice\":{\"lockPrice\":\"3.7E+8\",\"lockPriceStr\":\"0.5\",\"inPrice\":null,\"inPriceStr\":null,\"outPrice\":null,\"outPriceStr\":null,\"discountRate\":null,\"discountRateNum\":\"1.0\"},\"scenarios\":\"$1a\",\"modelTag\":[\"text-to-video\",\"image-to-video\",\"reference-to-video\"],\"inputTag\":null,\"outputTag\":null,\"apiUrl\":null,\"meta\":\"\",\"metaDescription\":\"Veo 3.1 Fast is a fast and cost-effective version of Google's Veo 3.1 AI video generation model that produces 4-8 second 1080p videos with synchronized native audio in under 60 seconds. It supports both text-to-video and image-to-video workflows for rapid content creation with cinematic motion and ambient sounds.\",\"extPriceModelConfig\":null,\"mediaUrl\":\"https://oss.gptproto.com/gptproto/ai-draw/java/test//2026/03/06/d298637ed21d4ad9b68949649e120725.mp4\",\"thumbUrl\":\"https://o